	   <tr><td colspan=2>if the weapons have better damage/delay then the pet does without weapons, then it will do something. for instance, if your pet does 8 damage max, and you give him a weapon with damage of 5, your pet will hit for 11 damage max instead. same goes for delay. pets always start out with a delay of 30, regardless of level, so once you get summon dagger go nuts with it, theyll ignore the crappy damage and use the awesome delay! same goes vice versa<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
